《'''亞森·羅蘋'''》（{{lang-en|''Lupin''}}）是一部[[法國|法國]][[推理片|推理]][[驚悚|驚悚]][[網路影集|網路影集]]，由{{link-en|喬治·凱|George Kay (writer)}}和{{link-fr|弗朗索瓦·烏贊|François Uzan}}開創，於2021年1月8日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]首播。本劇總共有十集，前五集於2021年1月播出<ref name="RT1">{{cite web |last1=Morris |first1=Lauren |title=When is French crime drama Lupin on Netflix? |url=https://www.radiotimes.com/news/tv/drama/2021-01-08/lupin-release-date-netflix/ |website=[[廣播時報|Radio Times]] |access-date=January 8, 2021 |date=January 8, 2021 |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108132100/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/tv/drama/2021-01-08/lupin-release-date-netflix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後五集於2021年6月11日播出<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Lupin’ To Return To Netflix Later This Summer|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/lupin-to-return-netflix-later-this-summer-1234682447/|last=White|first=Peter|website=[[Deadline|Deadline]]|date=2021-01-28|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815115941/https://deadline.com/2021/01/lupin-to-return-netflix-later-this-summer-1234682447/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Netflix已續訂本劇第三部<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ew.com/tv/omar-sy-lupin-season-3-preview-jaccuse/ |title=Lupin star Omar Sy gives updates on season 3 and the fate of J'accuse |last=Huff |first=Lauren |website=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2021-07-01 |access-date=July 8, 2021 |archive-date=2022-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220312180846/https://ew.com/tv/omar-sy-lupin-season-3-preview-jaccuse/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主角[[歐馬·希|歐馬·希]]演出的角色亞森·迪歐，靈感來源於1900年代早期[[莫理斯·盧布朗|莫理斯·盧布朗]]筆下的人物[[義賊|怪盜紳士]][[亞森·羅蘋|亞森·羅蘋]]<ref name="Polygon">{{cite web |title=The trailer for Netflix's Lupin introduces a new gentleman thief |url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/29/21493422/lupin-trailer-netflix-live-action-omar-sy |website=polygon.com |date=29 September 2020 |access-date=9 December 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001235117/https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/29/21493422/lupin-trailer-netflix-live-action-omar-sy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本劇在上線第一個月內就受到了7000萬家戶的收看，成為Netflix史上收視率最高的非[[英語|英語]]影集<ref>{{Cite web|last=Ravindran|first=Manori|date=January 21, 2021|title='Lupin' Will Be Seen By 70 Million Subscribers, Netflix Claims|url=https://variety.com/2021/tv/global/lupin-netflix-omar-sy-70-million-viewers-1234887688/|url-status=no|access-date=May 11, 2021|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|archive-date=2022-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331034214/https://variety.com/2021/tv/global/lupin-netflix-omar-sy-70-million-viewers-1234887688/}}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
亞森·迪歐是一位來到法國謀生的[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]移民的獨子。最初，亞森的父親被他的有錢有勢的老闆佩里格尼陷害偷了鑽石項鍊，在獄中上吊自殺，自此亞森變成了孤兒。25年過去了，受到父親留給他一本關於[[義賊|怪盜紳士]][[亞森·羅蘋|亞森·羅蘋]]的小說所啟發，亞森利用他的人格魅力，盜竊技術和偽裝等手段計劃揭露佩里格尼的罪行<ref name="Variety">{{cite web |title=Netflix Releases Premiere Date and Trailer for 'Lupin' Starring Omar Sy (TV News Roundup) |url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/tv-news-roundup-lupin-1234844314/ |website=variety.com |date=2 December 2020 |access-date=9 December 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202235309/https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/tv-news-roundup-lupin-1234844314/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Lupin trailer offers a fresh retelling of classic French gentleman thief |url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2020/12/a-suave-gentleman-thief-attempts-a-high-risk-heist-in-trailer-for-lupin/ |website=arstechnica.com |date=2 December 2020 |access-date=9 December 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203011956/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2020/12/a-suave-gentleman-thief-attempts-a-high-risk-heist-in-trailer-for-lupin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Lupin Trailer: Omar Sy Stars in Netflix's New Heist Series |url=https://www.comingsoon.net/tv/trailers/1156670-lupin-trailer |website=comingsoon.net |date=2 December 2020 |access-date=9 December 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202155556/https://www.comingsoon.net/tv/trailers/1156670-lupin-trailer |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Polygon" />。

