== 迴響 ==
=== 收視率 ===
《亞森·羅賓》是第一部進入美國Netflix前十名的法國影集，1月10日升至第三名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/lupin-first-french-series-netflix-us-top-ten-list-omar-sy-1234670905/ |title=Netflix’s 'Lupin' Becomes First French Series To Debut On Streamer’s U.S. Top Ten List |first=Nancy |last=Tartaglione |work=Deadline |date=January 11, 2011 |access-date=2021-09-13 |archive-date=2022-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123201616/https://deadline.com/2021/01/lupin-first-french-series-netflix-us-top-ten-list-omar-sy-1234670905/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。並在法國和[[德國|德國]]、[[奧地利|奧地利]]、[[義大利|義大利]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]、[[丹麥|丹麥]]等歐洲許多國家排名第一、還有[[瑞典|瑞典]]以及其他國家，如[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[巴西|巴西]]、[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]和[[南非|南非]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/sheenascott/2021/01/14/lupin-is-netflixs-most-popular-french-series-ever/ |title=‘Lupin’ Is Netflix’s Most Popular French Series |first=Sheena |last=Scott |date=January 14, 2021 |work=Forbes |access-date=2021-09-13 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130031044/https://www.forbes.com/sites/sheenascott/2021/01/14/lupin-is-netflixs-most-popular-french-series-ever/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

截至2021年1月31日，該劇累計共有7600萬家戶收看，成為繼《[[柏捷頓家族：名門韻事|柏捷頓家族：名門韻事]]》之後，Netflix原創節目有史以來第二大成功的處女作<ref>{{cite news |last1=Leonard |first1=Devin |title=How Netflix’s Lupin Pulled Off the Perfect Heist (Show) |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2021-06-29/how-netflix-s-lupin-and-omar-sy-pulled-off-the-perfect-heist-show |access-date=4 July 2021 |work=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]] |date=28 June 2021 |archive-date=2022-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323162456/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2021-06-29/how-netflix-s-lupin-and-omar-sy-pulled-off-the-perfect-heist-show |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vogue.in/culture-and-living/content/this-is-the-most-watched-show-on-netflix-right-now-and-its-not-what-you-think-lupin?amp |title=This is the most-watched show on Netflix right now and it’s not what you think |date=31 January 2021 |work=Vogue |access-date=1 February 2021 |quote=that’s more than The Queen’s Gambit and approaching Bridgerton levels of success |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305104401/https://www.vogue.in/culture-and-living/content/this-is-the-most-watched-show-on-netflix-right-now-and-its-not-what-you-think-lupin?amp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年4月Netflix透露，《亞森·羅賓》是當年第一季度該公司[[串流媒體|串流媒體]]服務中收視率最高的影集<ref>{{cite web|last1=Porter|first1=Rick|last2=McClintock|first2=Pamela|title='Lupin' snatches top Netflix viewing spot in first quarter|work=The Hollywood Reporter|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lupin-netflix-viewership-1st-quarter-2021|access-date=2021-09-13|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423014353/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lupin-netflix-viewership-1st-quarter-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

